short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Repository Analyzer performs an analysis of the contribution made by each individual developer on any public Github repository.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension performs an analysis of actual contribution for each developer and it helps to understand if an open source project is about to be abandoned.
It works on any public Github repository.
